## API Endpoints (`/api/*.js`)

All are Vercel serverless functions (ESM, `export default async function handler(req, res)`).

| File | Method | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `chat.js` | POST | Anthropic chat proxy |
| `elevenlabs.js` | POST | ElevenLabs TTS proxy |
| `vault-share-pin.js` | POST | Email vault PIN to family members via Resend |
| `family-connection-request.js` | POST | Email memorial owner when someone requests to join |
| `family-connection-approved.js` | POST | Email new family member after approval |
| `memorial-pdf.js` | POST | Generate memorial PDF (puppeteer) |
| `tribute-notification.js` | POST | Email owner when tribute is posted |
| `send-anniversary.js` | GET | Cron ‚Äî anniversary reminder emails |
| `vault-reset.js` | POST | Vault PIN reset (requires identity verification) |
| `stripe.js` | POST | Create Stripe checkout session |
| `stripe-webhook.js` | POST | Handle Stripe webhook events |
| `report-tribute.js` | POST | Report abusive tribute |
| `og.jsx` | GET | Open Graph image generation |
| `sitemap.js` | GET | Dynamic sitemap |

### vault-share-pin.js ‚Äî Request Shape
```json
{ "senderName": "Jane", "memorialName": "Ada Lovelace", "pin": "123456", "recipients": [{ "name": "Tom", "email": "tom@example.com" }] }
```

### family-connection-request.js ‚Äî Request Shape
```json
{ "ownerEmail": "...", "ownerName": "...", "claimerName": "...", "relation": "Son", "memorialName": "...", "verifyUrl": "https://whowasi.uk/family/verify?token=..." }
```

### family-connection-approved.js ‚Äî Request Shape
```json
{ "claimerEmail": "...", "claimerName": "...", "relation": "Son", "ownerName": "...", "memorialName": "..." }
```

