```
src/
  lib/
    instant.js        ‚Äî db initialisation
    vaultAuth.js      ‚Äî PIN hash/verify (SHA-256, localStorage, never server-side)
    uploadImage.js    ‚Äî Cloudinary upload helper
  pages/
    MemorialDetailPage.jsx   ‚Äî main memorial view (tabs: About, Photos, Tributes, Family, Vault)
    FamilyTreePage.jsx       ‚Äî orbital family tree
    LegacyLettersPage.jsx    ‚Äî vault (letters, docs, PIN sharing)
    DashboardPage.jsx        ‚Äî user dashboard (memorials + family messages)
    FamilyVerifyPage.jsx     ‚Äî /family/verify?token= (approve/reject connections)
    JoinFamilyPage.jsx       ‚Äî /join (claim family membership via invite code)
    LegalPages.jsx           ‚Äî Privacy Policy + Terms of Service (UK GDPR / DPA 2018)
  components/
    orbital/FamilyTreeOrb.jsx        ‚Äî canvas orbital animation
    shared/FamilyMessagesSection.jsx ‚Äî private family messages thread
    ui/VaultDocuments.jsx            ‚Äî vault document list (isOwner prop)
```

