## Deployment Checklist

### First-time / after schema changes
```bash
# 1. Push InstantDB schema (new entities/fields)
npx instant-cli push schema

# 2. Push InstantDB permissions
npx instant-cli push perms

# 3. Deploy to Vercel
vercel --prod
```

### Routine deploy
```bash
npm run build            # verify clean build first
vercel --prod
```

### Local dev
```bash
npm run dev              # Vite dev server on :5173
vercel dev               # Vite + Vercel functions together on :3000 (preferred)
```
